apps.localizedDescription:
This tweak makes Spotify think you have a Premium subscription, granting free listening, just like Spotilife, and provides some additional features like custom lyrics.

The following features will not work, EVER:
- Very High audio quality
- Native playlist downloading (you can download podcast episodes though)
- Jam (hosting a Spotify Jam and joining it remotely requires Premium; only joining in-person works)
apps.name: EeveeSpotify

apps.localizedDescription:
Feather is a free on-device iOS application manager/installer built with UIKit for quality.

Features:

Altstore repo support. Supporting Legacy and 2.0 repo structures
Import your own .ipa's.
Inject tweaks when signing apps.
Install applications straight to your device seamlessly over the air.
Allows multiple certificate imports for easy switching.
Configurable signing options. (name, bundleid, version, other plist options)
Meant to be used with Apple Accounts that are apart of ADP (Apple Developer Program). however other certificates can also work!
Easy resigning! If you have another certificate you would like to use on an app you may resign and reinstall that same app!
No tracking, analytics, or any of the sort. Your information such as UDID and certificates will never leave the device.
apps.name: Feather

apps.localizedDescription:
Sign application for iOS is a software tool that enables users to sign documents electronically using their Apple devices, such as iPhones and iPads.

Typically, these applications allow users to:
1. Upload Documents: Import PDFs or other document types from various sources, including email, cloud storage, or directly from the device.
2. Sign Documents: Utilize touch or stylus input to create a digital signature, which can be saved for future use.
3. Form Filling: Fill out forms and add text, checkboxes, and other annotations to documents.
4. Secure Signing: Ensure document integrity through encryption and authentication methods, often including options for secure authentication.
5. Tracking and Notifications: Provide functionalities to track document status, send reminders, and notify parties when documents are signed.
6. Integration: Many eSign apps integrate with other software solutions like document management systems, email clients, and productivity tools.
apps.name: E-Sign

apps.localizedDescription:
iTorrent is an ordinary torrent client for iOS with Files app support.

What can this app do:

• Download in the background
• Sequential download (use VLC to watch films while loading)
• Add torrent files from Share menu (Safari and other apps)
• Add magnet links directly from Safari
• Store files in Files app (iOS 11+)
• File sharing directly from app
• Download torrent by link
• Download torrent by magnet
• Send notification on torrent downloaded
• FTP Server (unstable)
• Select files to download or not
• Change UI to dark theme

Now supporting these localizations:
• English
• Russian
• Turkish
